To compile the application with production version with debug messages in Guang Da Qi Huo trading environment (speculator account):
$ make application SPFLAG=PRODUCTION DFLAG=DEBUG BFLAG=BROKER_GD THFLAG=TICKERHEAD_IF XFLAG=EXCHANGE_CFFEX SAHFLAG=ACCOUNT_SPECULATOR

To compile the application with production version with debug messages in Zhong Da Qi Huo trading environment (hedger account):
$ make application SPFLAG=PRODUCTION DFLAG=DEBUG BFLAG=BROKER_ZD THFLAG=TICKERHEAD_IF XFLAG=EXCHANGE_CFFEX SAHFLAG=ACCOUNT_HEDGER

To compile the application with production version without debug messages in Guang Da Qi Huo trading environment (arbitrager account):
$ make application SPFLAG=PRODUCTION DFLAG=NDEBUG BFLAG=BROKER_GD THFLAG=TICKERHEAD_IF XFLAG=EXCHANGE_CFFEX SAHFLAG=ACCOUNT_ARBITRAGER

To compile the application with production version without debug messages in Guang Da Qi Huo trading environment (speculator account):
$ make application SPFLAG=PRODUCTION DFLAG=NDEBUG BFLAG=BROKER_GD THFLAG=TICKERHEAD_IF XFLAG=EXCHANGE_CFFEX SAHFLAG=ACCOUNT_SPECULATOR

To run all the unit tests with simulation version (speculator account):
$ make test SPFLAG=SIMULATION DFLAG=NDEBUG BFLAG=BROKER_GD THFLAG=TICKERHEAD_IF XFLAG=EXCHANGE_CFFEX SAHFLAG=ACCOUNT_SPECULATOR

To clean up the object files and executable files:
$ make clean

Pay attention to the following comments in the source files:
$ /* TODO */
$ /* TOCHECK */


Please set the following environment variables in your .bashrc or .profile
export ZZTRADERBIN=path..to..futures_trade/src
export ZZDATAROOT=path..to..futures_trade..data
export ZZDATAOUT=path..to..futures_trade..simulation..output
export ZZCONFIG=path..to..futures_trade/config
